{"tid":730901,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"謝霆鋒賣餅乾出事 食安中心勒令下架","createTime":"2018-07-05T19:19:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T02:26:13.000Z","uid":52658,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"33744ca9ff758e558efea8edf7bd1a609037f6b7","tid":730901,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T19:19:58.000Z","msg":"香港食物安全中心近日嚴格把關，4日前往謝霆鋒開設的「鋒味」做檢測，其中招牌曲奇餅的產品標示中顯示，每100克含3克的糖，實際檢測後發現，每100克竟含有17.6克的糖，等於超出標示5倍，相關單位已通知店家將該項產品下架停售。<br />\n<br />\n隨後謝霆鋒也透過臉書發表聲明，表示這次是香港食安中心個別抽樣調查的情況，並非「鋒味」的安全質量出現問題，目前已將食品樣本交給另一化驗所重新檢驗，在結果出爐前會暫時將該產品下架。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d50369e3ff292c1690b8ead885d2cc4bd32a1ef","tid":730901,"uid":183302,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T05:25:59.000Z","msg":"太性感了"},{"pid":"409637c0e241aa1e88d2d9fea572ac6666043ffd","tid":730901,"uid":92278,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T05:28:06.000Z","msg":"diu垃圾"},{"pid":"4bfd04136117669fe35dfa30caa8b03b706a15b5","tid":730901,"uid":1067,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T05:31:07.000Z","msg":"他知道，下架是沒有用的"},{"pid":"b97947e3e4f4887bf13e10e8fbdf8ca40dd4a75a","tid":730901,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bfd04136117669fe35dfa30caa8b03b706a15b5","tid":730901,"uid":1067,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T05:31:07.000Z","msg":"他知道，下架是沒有用的"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T05:32:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a0976d111404da2936d504f1b73902343216bf","tid":730901,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bfd04136117669fe35dfa30caa8b03b706a15b5","tid":730901,"uid":1067,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T05:31:07.000Z","msg":"他知道，下架是沒有用的"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T05:33:53.000Z","msg":"他知道 賣餅乾是沒有用的<img src=\"/assets/faces/no